            <section id="story">
                <p>They said it would never happen, but here we are. The year is 2031 and mankind's thirst for a cure to cancer has led to a zombie apocalypse. A horde of elderly zombies have taken over Ronnie's gym, but that won't stop our fearless hero. Your mission: get Ronnie to 100 protein points by collecting milk cartons. Or die trying.</p>
            </section>    
            <hr>
            <section id="controls">
               <p>Controls: Move left with arrow key left -- move right with arrow key right -- move up with arrow key up -- move down with arrow key down</p>
            </section>    
